{"tid":2196713,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"毒品調查科拘捕15人涉利用whatsapp溝通 操控壹傳媒股價","createTime":"2020-09-10T06:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T06:32:06.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"33555eae0619cc949728ce93e31fc7246e1c540c","tid":2196713,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:01:02.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒股價早前異動，警方拘捕15人涉串謀詐騙及洗黑錢。消息指，毒品調查科拘捕15人涉嫌利用whatsapp作溝通工具，透過買賣壹傳媒股票，舞高弄低股價，高位獲利，其中一名被捕人更從中獲利超過2500萬港元，警方會在今日下午4時在警察總部交代案件詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，警方一直正視操縱市場的問題，並會對任何詐騙行為進行全面調查，亦會考慮對有關人等控以盜竊、串謀行騙等罪名，被告一經定罪，可被判14年監禁。"},{"pid":"36cbf143f34e789744253c3224da2e5d91341f38","tid":2196713,"uid":201604,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:01:40.000Z","msg":"黑警毒品調查科=正常公司既採購部"},{"pid":"39ad16747c255cd79c3f6585b98e3fe59380d377","tid":2196713,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"關毒品調查科咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"534381b86e98a0f42aaa40d5d6ef10db2281c229","tid":2196713,"uid":112581,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"39ad16747c255cd79c3f6585b98e3fe59380d377","tid":2196713,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"關毒品調查科咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"得毒品調查科有貨<br />\n遲d就會話15人藏毒"},{"pid":"1fd7309aded86a5031104892846e248fbb950d5f","tid":2196713,"uid":2480,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:11:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706203083129d173fe09e1f86eaf165d03867a8c","tid":2196713,"uid":143499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d1efc517d22125ee0c411a1cb8a27e912c5af83","tid":2196713,"uid":121197,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"